descriptionHtml:
Dr. Smily Pruthi MBBS, MD, is the Author of best selling book “Conceptual Review of Biochemistry”. In her years of teaching experience, he has helped thousands of UG, PG and FMGE aspirants.



With the launch of this app she aims to make sure you never cram Biochemistry again, understand the concepts and fall in love with the subject.


App includes video lectures covering the entire Biochemistry, Tests with Video Discussion, Question Bank, Free daily updates and much more.
descriptionShort: Clear your concepts in Biochemistry and fall in love with the subject.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Hello Doctor,
While you've been working to serve the nation in these tough times, we've been working to serve you and upping your learning experience.
Introducing Key Features:
•An interactive Home Screen to provide Quick Links to your most accessed content
•Treasures, for the last-minute reads
•Let's Start Preparing with all the Videos, Qbanks and Treasures in 1 place
•Read Notes while Watching Videos in the same screen
•An independent Test Screen
•Enhanced Menu and personalised Setting options
